{"tid":1300361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN五日前新聞原來已經講左，美國副總統五日前新緊急改行程，今日睇番原來要見黎智英。","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:00:45.000Z","uid":43785,"like":965,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"d5895f8e066317b29d03c5d87ad30a76144aac7f","tid":1300361,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-080325164.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%258E-080325164.html&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7PSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ebf5460b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-080325164.html</a><br />\n彭斯突被要求留守華府 原因不明<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯，原本美東時間星期二，要到美國「新罕布什爾州」出席一場公開行程，不過福斯新聞網報導，彭斯啟程之後，突然臨時被召回；然而，美國白宮副總統辦公室則說，彭斯只是臨時改變行程，他甚至根本還沒有離開華府。外界一些捕風捉影的報導，已經造成外界的困惑，與不實資訊流傳（葉柏毅報導）<br />\n<br />\n福斯新聞網率先報導，彭斯原本預定星期二，要到美國新罕布什爾州一間治療藥物成癮中心，宣導抵抗藥物濫用的重要性。不過，彭斯的專機「空軍二號」在起飛後不久，突然被緊急召回華府；而有白宮官員向美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）表示，彭斯「確實折返華府」，不過「並不是因為任何緊急狀況」，但是CNN的消息來源也沒有透露，彭斯為什麼臨時被召回華府。然而，彭斯辦公室發言人，在稍後出面澄清時，卻又把整件事輕描淡寫，發言人表示，彭斯確實是在啟程之前，突然被要求臨時留在華府，只是把行程改期，而空軍二號甚至還沒有起飛，但是發言人又強調，「沒有任何緊急狀況」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gx5LZ4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgx5LZ4T.jpg&h=00068e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是，CNN在報導中說，如果副總統臨時被發出緊急要求，必須留在華府，通常不是因為「總統出現了重大健康問題」，就是「有重大國安狀況」，總之，情況絕對不單純。<br />\n<br />\n然而，彭斯辦公室一方面證實，彭斯確實被要求改變原訂行程，留在華府，卻又說沒有任何重大狀況，外界不需緊張，這種前後矛盾的訊息，連常駐白宮的老媒體記者，都覺得「未免太不可思議」。"},{"pid":"c06ada61e14caaf7991a98dfa92d5b6deb7276b0","tid":1300361,"uid":62749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c1bc115cd4883cfbf5d8f75ed04e8020edca53","tid":1300361,"uid":43785,"like":291,"dislike":1,"score":290,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"原來要見黎志英"},{"pid":"82990996a06daa1cc98c51a03731b373fd3f31d1","tid":1300361,"uid":75,"like":566,"dislike":1,"score":565,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"當係為咗肥佬黎先<br />\n<br />\n咁俾面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52400d4296c1d7695b3548356633e7cabee9fb38","tid":1300361,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b6b2a73ea9077715f196611a0fa5cdd172e6739","tid":1300361,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a193d5d4da3143ec4fd6dc8df18d51a39dd301e9","tid":1300361,"uid":265066,"like":471,"dislike":0,"score":471,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1PgrKyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1PgrKyC.jpg&h=0d210409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abd92a1852f64becb9cb4dec7317b8812410e9f0","tid":1300361,"uid":19557,"like":320,"dislike":0,"score":320,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"咁不可思義既改行程原來係見黎智英 今鋪中共有冇d 腳軟"},{"pid":"52be0a9b2bf67bc8003aeeaa5581372c38ec1dd7","tid":1300361,"uid":37528,"like":320,"dislike":0,"score":320,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"我都好希望係，不過有無咁誇張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.